      • init

        public static void init(Context context)
        Initializes REST Client. Before invoking this method you should insert meta-data entry with API key in AndroidManifest file. The entry should look like the following: For more information how to set up API Key refer to Android SDK documentation. Please, read also REST API documentation before interacting with RESTClient.
        Parameters:
        context - the context
        See Also:
        kontakt.io REST API docs, Android SDK - meta-data entry

      • newInstance

        Creates new instance of REST Client. If the REST Client is not set up, method will throw IllegalStateException.
        Returns:
        the rest client
